Name: Catch Your Kitty
About the game: You move a cat that catches kitties. Kitties are thrown down by birds. The Number of casts and birds increases during the game. You can not move all cats at the same time. You must switch between cats. Update (04.04.2020) - The number of cats increases faster (every 2 levels; before every 8 levels)
